  - verses:
    - title: A Vision of Locusts
      content: "The Sovereign <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> showed me a vision. I saw
        him preparing to send a vast swarm of locusts over the land. This was after
        the king\u2019s share had been harvested from the fields and as the main
        crop was coming up. "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "In my vision the locusts ate every green plant in sight. Then I said,
        \u201CO Sovereign <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t, please forgive us or we
        will not survive, for Israel[COMMENT[0]] is so small.\u201D  "
      comments:
